{"name":"地信","postlist":[{"title":"ArcMap10.6从世界地图扣取东亚及东南亚国家地图","slug":"ArcMap10.6从世界地图扣取东亚及东南亚国家地图","date":"2018-09-27T12:10:44.000Z","updated":"2022-01-08T02:16:28.392Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ArcMap10.6从世界地图扣取东亚及东南亚国家地图.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/liaochenlanruo/cdn@master/img/custom/papers/worldmap.jpg","content":"<p>在发表文章需要用到我们的地图时，有时候需要将咱们的地图和东南亚地区合并在一起。这些工作可以利用 ArcMap 完成。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<ol>\n<li>Word map 下载（<a href=\"https://gadm.org/download_world.html%EF%BC%89\">https://gadm.org/download_world.html）</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/liaochenlanruo/cdn@master/img/custom/papers/worldmap.jpg\" class=\"lazyload placeholder\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/liaochenlanruo/cdn@master/img/custom/papers/worldmap.jpg\" srcset=\"https://img2.baidu.com/it/u=2037979560,2772131037&fm=26&fmt=auto&gp=0.jpg\" alt=\"world map download\" /></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>将 “gadm36_0.shp” 导入 ArcMap 10.7</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>左边的图层上右键 ——open attribute table</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在打开的属性表中通过 Ctrl 键多选如下 FID：</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">22</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">34</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">35</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">43</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">102</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">104</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">115</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">116</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">118</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">119</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">122</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">124</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">147</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">149</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">157</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">168</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">172</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">176</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">181</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">189</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">194</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">218</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">219</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">222</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">228</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">241</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">250</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">251</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>\n<p>关闭属性表</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>右键单击图层，选择”Data——Export Data“，导出选中区域的 shp 文件</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>在 https://mapshaper.org/ 上可以将 shp 转换为 Geojson 格式绘制地图</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"地信","path":"api/categories/地信.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"地图","path":"api/tags/地图.json"}]},{"title":"设置元素加载时间解决D3.js文字被图像覆盖的问题","slug":"设置元素加载时间解决D3.js文字被图像覆盖的问题","date":"2018-08-23T03:13:00.000Z","updated":"2022-01-08T02:16:28.469Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/设置元素加载时间解决D3.js文字被图像覆盖的问题.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>在绘制地图的时候，常常需要添加饼图，柱状图以及文字等。经常发现添加的元素被地图背景覆盖，无论在 html 文档中如何调整元素的顺序都没有用，百思不得其解。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>D3.js 默认按照代码顺序加载元素，后来想明白了，地图背景加载比较慢，而文字等小元素加载很快，导致小元素先被加载，背景元素后来加载进而覆盖在小元素之上。解决的思路就是给小元素设置加载时间，让其在背景元素加载完之后再加载，用到的是 “setTimeout” 函数。</p>\n<p><strong>具体用法如下：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">setTimeout<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function-name function\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n      小元素的执行代码写在此处\n                       <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>, <span class=\"token number\">3000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>//延迟3s执行<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"地信","path":"api/categories/地信.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"地图","path":"api/tags/地图.json"}]}]}